---
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 px-4 bg-surface">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-title font-bold text-primary mb-4">
        Sound Familiar?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lead text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        You've been fighting these battles alone. It's time to get the tools that actually work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Problem/Solution blocks -->
    <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
      <!-- Block 1: Problem left, Solution right -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center" data-reveal>
        <div class="bg-white/80 rounded-2xl p-7 border-l-4 border-text-muted/30 shadow-card">
          <p class="text-lg text-text-main leading-relaxed italic">
            <span class="text-2xl text-text-muted font-heading">"</span>coworker said I just had a little headache<span class="text-2xl text-text-muted font-heading">"</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-3">— After witnessing vomiting and panic attacks from migraines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border-l-4 border-accent shadow-card">
          <p class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">The Problem:</p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            MigraWork gives you the documentation to prove your "little headache" is a disability protected under ADA. Our templates include migraine-specific severity explanations that make it impossible for employers to claim they "didn't understand."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Block 2: Solution left, Problem right (alternating) -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center" data-reveal>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border-l-4 border-accent shadow-card order-2 md:order-1">
          <p class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">The Problem:</p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Stop apologizing for your symptoms. MigraWork provides manager conversation scripts written by employment lawyers — so you can advocate for yourself without feeling like you're "making a scene."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/80 rounded-2xl p-7 border-l-4 border-text-muted/30 shadow-card order-1 md:order-2">
          <p class="text-lg text-text-main leading-relaxed italic">
            <span class="text-2xl text-text-muted font-heading">"</span>I wish I never worried about being loud and wrong whenever I felt like it.<span class="text-2xl text-text-muted font-heading">"</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Block 3: Problem left, Solution right -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center" data-reveal>
        <div class="bg-white/80 rounded-2xl p-7 border-l-4 border-text-muted/30 shadow-card">
          <p class="text-lg text-text-main leading-relaxed italic">
            <span class="text-2xl text-text-muted font-heading">"</span>I'm so tired of fighting<span class="text-2xl text-text-muted font-heading">"</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border-l-4 border-accent shadow-card">
          <p class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">The Solution:</p>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            We've done the fighting for you. Every template is pre-written, legally reviewed for your state, and designed to get approval the first time — not buried in HR paperwork that's never answered.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
